<PolicyPage
  title="AI Usage Policy"
  description="How AI tools may be used in the editorial workflow."
>
  <p>
    AI tools may be used to support research organization, outlines, editing, formatting, or technical site maintenance. Human editorial review is required before publication.
  </p>
  <p>
    AI output should not be treated as a source. Facts, dates, quotes, statistics, and claims should be checked against reliable sources before they appear in published articles.
  </p>
</PolicyPage>
